description: Stressful times for many people at the moment cuz of #covid19 Let’s not let our imaginations take control of us. Try and focus only on what YOU have control over; and what you CANNOT control? Let fate take its course. Whatever happens, things always work out one way or another. And worrying about it wont do jack shit! Ps. Dont listen to too much media #fearmongering should be a crime!
